71	/// A builder for initializing a liveliness subscription.
72	///
73	/// The builder is returned by the [`Liveliness::declare_subscriber`](crate::liveliness::Liveliness::declare_subscriber) method and
74	/// resolves to the [`Subscriber`] receiving the liveliness samples.
75	///
76	/// # Examples
77	/// ```
78	/// # #[tokio::main]
